headline: Assessing MSCI (MSCI) Valuation As Earnings Approach And Greece Reclassification Consultation Gains Focus
summary: Why MSCI (MSCI) Is In Focus Right Now MSCI (MSCI) is in the spotlight as it prepares to report earnings this Wednesday, while also asking investors for feedback on a possible upgrade of Greece from emerging to developed market status.
